flowchart TD
  A([Start]) --> B{Endpoint}
  B -->|GET /inventory| C[Load inventory projection]
  C --> D[Return inventory]

  B -->|Hero upgrade/evolve| E[Validate hero state and costs]
  E --> F{Enough resources?}
  F -->|No| X[Return insufficient resources]
  F -->|Yes| G[Apply stat or tier mutation]
  G --> H[Persist inventory and player state]
  H --> I[Log reward or cost transaction]
  I --> J[Return updated hero]

  B -->|Skill purchase/upgrade| K[Validate config and ownership]
  K --> L[Apply purchase or level up]
  L --> H

  D --> Z([End])
  J --> Z
  X --> Z
